data.description: Welcome to Winchester! In the cul-de-sac of a short street w/only 6 homes, you'll find a meticulously maintained, one owner 3 bed 2.5 bath home. Did I mention the impossible to find BASEMENT and .46 acre lot?  Walking through the door you feel home. On the main level you will enjoy the many gathering spaces for family in friends! A living room, family room and separate dining area ensure space for all. Enjoy meals in the eat in kitchen, or your dining room! Looking into the large backyard you’ll enjoy the trees providing privacy. The upper deck is perfect for meals and time spent outdoors. Upstairs you’ll find a primary suite w/ walk-in closet and ensuite. Additionally, are two l bedrooms and an office w/ closet that easily becomes bedroom #4.  A second full bath completes the upstairs.  The  elusive heated and cooled basement provides over 900 sq feet of possibilities!! An additional patio on the basement level allows even more opportunities to explore and enjoy your private backyard.
